by gorry/py gorry
Homonym Number:
Word Class: exclamation
Sense Number:
Definition:stage Maori for by golly! (rather than <i>by God!</i>); (HO never heard this used seriously or unconsciously by a Maori)


Origin: [none]
Register: informal

Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: also by korry/py korry
